					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Jennifer Acker</h4>
												<p>Jennifer Acker is founder and Editor-in-Chief of The Common. Short stories, translations, and essays have appeared in The Washington Post, Guernica, n+1, Ploughshares, The Journal, The Literary Review, Ascent, Sonora Review, Harper’s, The Millions, The New Inquiry, and Publishers Weekly, among other places. Her debut novel The Limits of the World will be published in April 2019.</p>
